	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />If you want an MKE&lt;-&gt;IDE interface, you'll have to do it yourself. The GameStations with IDE drives do not convert MKE to IDE as previously thought; they have new IDE registers and patched the GD ROM to use that instead.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


