		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />It's not possible without using a microcontroller and latches to translate MKE to IDE. MKE is proprietary and to my knowledge barely documented online, IMO it's not really worth reverse engineering now.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


