	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />It can certainly take CD-Rs, but probably not CD-RWs. 
<br />
<br />IIRC discs need to be Mode 1, ISO9660 only (no Joliet), 8.3 filenames (level 1), no directories. I'm not sure about the character set, you're using DOS right? I don't believe multisession settings matter.
<br />
<br />It looks to me like your image should work... try ISO9660 charset though.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


